Dark forces are at work in this devilishly good Praline Porter. Toffee and chocolate unite and come a-knocking. Open up to layers of smooth roastycharacter, with notes of vanilla, mellow coffee and a subtle nuttiness. And a bitter sweet cliffhanger finale.
